\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 7. H. viscosum} (Willk.) P. Silva,{\i  Agron. Lusit. }{\b 24}: 165 (1964) ({\i H. umbellatum} var.{\i  viscosum} Willk.). Like {\b 6} but 25-60 cm; branches more or less straight, suberect; leaves 10-20 mm, distributed along the branches; flowers in 3-5 whorls, each of (-4)5-6(-9) flowers; pedicels more or less unequal; sepals hirsute-villous.{\i  C., S. & E. Spain, E. Portugal.} Hs Lu.
